        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="internal-banner__content">
                <h1 class="heading-3">The Springs Souk</h1>
                <p class="sub-title">The Springs Souk is a contemporary and perfectly planned destination delivering exceptional retail, leisure, and lifestyle experiences to residents and visitors of multiple communities, including The Springs, The Meadows, The Lakes, Emirates Hills, The Views, The Greens communities, as well as to neighbouring Al Barsha. Two levels of retail and entertainment mix showcase restaurants, cafes, fashion and accessories, a laundromat, a supermarket, ATMS, pharmacies, a clinic, a money exchange, Reel Cinemas, and children’s shops.</p>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center gap-4">
          <div class='d-flex gap-3 app-popover-icons'>
                      </div>
                  </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

